Upload all four files to your S3 bucket root.Final Step: Test Your ApplicationVisit your S3 website endpoint URL.
Subscribe with a real email → check inbox/spam for confirmation link.
Confirm subscription.
Create a test event → you should receive an email notification.
Refresh the page → new event appears in the list.

Done! You now have a working serverless event announcement system.

